NEW STORE OPENING SOON! ALL POSITIONS AVAILABLE!<br>
<br>
Please join us for a job fair with onsite interview happening:<br>
<br>
<br>
DATE: Tuesday, March 28 through Saturday April 1<br>
TIME: 10:00 am to 6:00 pm  <br>
JOB FAIR LOCATION: 600 Central Ave, Highland Park IL 60035<br>
JOBS AVAILABLE: Team Member, Shift Leads, Dough Maker, Pizza Smith<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Already a hit in Southern California, with 5 locations in Florida, 11 locations in Illinois and lines out the door, Blaze Fast-Fire'd Pizza is a new fast-casual dining concept that serves custom-built artisanal pizzas at lightning speeds!<br>
<br>
<br>
The job fair takes place from 10 am to 6 pm, Tuesday March 28th  through Saturday April 1st for our NEW Highland Park location. The store is located at 600 Central Ave, Highland Park, IL 60035. We are looking for Part-time and Full-time employees for all shifts. If you are friendly, personable and ready to take a bold new step, we want to speak with you. The only prior experience you'll need is a great smile, interest in food and to become a team member. If you are a positive and enthusiastic person looking for an amazing opportunity, we encourage you to apply and learn more about our organization. We think you'll quickly see that Blaze Pizza "gets it" with both its pizzas and people.<br>
<br>
Please apply online before coming to job fair at www.work4blazepizza.com <br>
<br>
<br>
What is Blaze? Ok, we're gonna keep this quick. Because exceptional quality at lightning speed is what we're all about. Blaze Pizza. Head food guy, Executive Chef Bradford Kent (aka "The Pizza Whisperer"). Fresh, made-from-scratch dough. Healthful, artisanal ingredients on the assembly line. Inventive to classic. You decide. Blazing hot oven + dedicated pizzasmith + 180 sec perfectly crisp perfection.<br>
<a href="https://youtu.be/TdClkM57KQo" rel="nofollow">https://youtu.be/TdClkM57KQo</a> <br>
<br>
If you are not able to come to the job fair, please apply online at: <a href="https://secure.jobappnetwork.com/apply/c_bpz/l_en/hourly.go#s" rel="nofollow">https://secure.jobappnetwork.com/apply/c_bpz/l_en/hourly.go#s</a>  <br>
<br>
If you are friendly and personable and are ready to take a bold new step, we'd like to meet you!<br>
    </section>

